Customer: Hello.

Customer: Ek bhi lead nahi dikh raha hai na unme se.
Customer: Ha.
Customer: Ek do dikh jata hai lekin jo commitment hai na aapka weekly 70 wo fulfill nahi ho raha hai.
Executive: Okay. Thik hai sir weekly aise nahi hai ki 70 aapko properly aayegi main samajh raha hu aap jo kehna chah rahe ho. Main ek kam karta hu aap mere ko 10 minute ka time denge main ek bar ek bar connect karwata hu aapko abhi system pe available hai na aap?
Customer: Main hu. Hello.
Executive: Ji ji main hu available.
Executive: Achcha bas mere ko aap 10 minute ka time dijiye main ek bar video meet arrange karwata hu aapse properly ek bar ek ek cheez ka discuss kar lenge aapse.
Customer: Thik hai sir mere ko 10 minute ka ek time dijiye aap.
Executive: Main aapko connect karta hu. Thik hai sir.
